{"type":null,"faqId":9641,"title":"荣耀畅玩版（g750-t01）蓝牙与电脑连接上网，蓝牙传输文件","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>支持与电脑共享网络，支持蓝牙游戏。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-18pt;text-align:justify;\">\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机支持</span><span>PAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（</span><span>Personal Area Network Profile</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">），支持其他设备共享手机的网络资源。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在<b>设置</b></span><span> <span>&gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">更多</span></b><span><span>...&gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络共享与便携式热点</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中，勾选<b>蓝牙共享网络</b>；接受对方发起的连接后，即可建立自己的个人局域网络。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>设置界面：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30110\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:26.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>“更多”界面：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:26.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30112\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:26.25pt;\">\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:26.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>“移动网络共享”界面：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:26.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30113\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:26.25pt;\">\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-18pt;text-align:justify;\">\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>手机支持蓝牙游戏。此功能更多取决于三方应用的设计，一般的步骤为：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-18pt;text-align:justify;\">\n\t<span><span><span>a.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在游戏中选择搜索其他蓝牙设备</span><span>;</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-18pt;text-align:justify;\">\n\t<span><span><span>b.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">找到你连接的蓝牙设备预置配对</span><span>OK</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">；</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-18pt;text-align:justify;\">\n\t<span><span><span>c.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>开始游戏；</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>（各种支持蓝牙的游戏操作步骤不一定一样，截图以一款下载的象棋游戏为背景）</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>G750</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">作为服务端创建对局截图：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入游戏</span><span><span> &gt; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">联机</span><span><span> &gt; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">创建对局：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30114\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>点击“确定”后：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30115\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>选择“允许”后，会开启蓝牙可见性，等待其他手机接入游戏：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30118\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>其他手机选择此手机后，出现配对请求：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30119\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>选择“配对”后，连接成功，可以开始游戏。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30121\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>G750</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">作为客户端加入其他对局截图：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入游戏</span><span><span> &gt; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">联机</span><span><span> &gt; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">加入对局</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30123\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">搜索到设备后，选择相应的设备“</span><span><span>HUAWEI G750-T00</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”出现配对请求：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30124\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>选择“配对”后，连接成功，可以开始游戏。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30128\" /> \n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"226","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396259345000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":153,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"蓝牙","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}